07:59.771 --> 08:02.065
Hi, Nguyen-Nguyen.
Um, everything all right?

08:02.691 --> 08:05.902
Yes. Using Forkoontula as ice pick.

08:05.986 --> 08:09.030
If ice not dead before, it dead now.

08:09.114 --> 08:10.532
Um...

08:10.615 --> 08:13.910
[sighs] Listen, I was returning
your casserole dish the other night

08:13.994 --> 08:15.495
and, uh...

08:15.578 --> 08:18.540
