She says things.

09:10.842 --> 09:11.885
Right, Sue?

09:12.802 --> 09:15.221
Yeah. Must be the heat.

09:15.305 --> 09:17.515
No, no, no. I'm sorry.

09:17.599 --> 09:19.934
Fourth of July is all about America,

09:20.018 --> 09:22.937
but I wanted Nguyen-Nguyen
to feel included too.

09:23.021 --> 09:26.775
So, I encouraged her to make a meal
that reminds her of who she is,

09:26.858 --> 09:29.736
the village she came from,
the family she lost,

09:29.819 --> 09:32.822
and the homeland
she so desperately misses.

09:32.906 --> 09:35.200
